Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不想去社团
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
